<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css">

    <style>
        body {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            display: block;
            padding: 0px;
            margin: 0px;
            overflow: unset;
            font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .md {
            padding-left: 35px;
            padding-right: 35px;
            padding-bottom: 80px;
        }

        .konfirmasi {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
        }

        .biodata {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .link {
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: rgb(56, 56, 56);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .right {
            margin-right: 100px;
        }

        .tag {
            padding-left: 20px;
            padding-right: 20px;
            background-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);
            border-radius: 5px;
            color: black;
            font-weight: 600;
            width: 180px;
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .web-lab {
            text-decoration: unset;
            color: rgb(100, 131, 235);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .web-lab:hover {
            color: rgb(36, 84, 243);
        }

        p {
            color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.885);
            text-align: left;
        }

        table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
            width: 100%;
        }

        td,
        th {
            font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
            font-weight: unset;
            text-align: left;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            padding-right: 8px;
        }

        .card {
            max-width: 600px;
            display: block;
            position: absolute;
            background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .logo-lab {
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .banner {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .section {
            width: 100%;
            table-layout: fixed;
            padding-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .telegram {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            padding-top: 8px;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .whatsapp {
            width: 35px;
            height: 35px;
            padding-top: 5px;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .text1 {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
            padding-top: 13px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .text2 {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
            padding-top: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            p {
                color: black;
                display: block;
            }

            .link {
                display: block;
                padding-left: 0px;
                padding-right: 0px;
            }

            .right {
                margin-right: 0px;
            }

            .tag {
                text-align: center;
                padding-right: 0;
                padding-left: 43px;
            }

            .text1 {
                padding-top: 16px;
            }

            .text2 {
                padding-top: 18px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <center class="section">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="logo-lab">
                <img class="banner" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vysf/usefull-photos/main/logo-lab.jpg"
                    alt="logo-lab" />
            </div>
            <div class="md">
                <p class="p">
                    Yth <span>mahasiswa/i</span> <br /><br />
                    Data kamu sudah berhasil terdaftar. Silahkan cek data pendaftaran
                    kamu di
                    <a href="https://www.labfisikauntan.com" class="web-lab">web laboratorium fisika untan</a>.
                    Terima
                    kasih telah mendaftar.
                </p>
                <hr />
                <p>
                    <span class="konfirmasi">Pendaftaran Praktikum Fisika Dasar</span>
                </p>
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Nama Lengkap</th>
                        <th>{{nama}}</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>NIM</th>
                        <th>{{nim}}</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Program Studi</th>
                        <th>{{prodi}}</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Praktikum</th>
                        <th>{{praktikum}}</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Keterangan</th>
                        <th>{{keterangan}}</th>
                    </tr>
                </table>
                <hr />
                <p class="p2">
                    Jika ada kesalahan dalam pengisian data segera lapor ke Laboratorium
                    Fisika Dasar. Untuk info lebih lanjut dapat menghubungi link dibawah
                    ini.
                </p>
                <div class="link">
                    <p class="tag right">
                        <img class="whatsapp" style="text-align: center;"
                            src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vysf/usefull-photos/main/logo%20wa.png"
                            alt="logo whatsapp">
                        <span class="text2">+6285159202046</span>
                    </p>
                    <p class="tag">
                        <img class="telegram" style="text-align: center;"
                            src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vysf/usefull-photos/main/logo%20telegram.png"
                            alt="logo telegram">
                        <span class="text1">t.me/labfisikadasar</span>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </center>

</body>

</html>